<br>
Requirements can be found <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://hoc.eq.tripod.com" target="top">here</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> in the Guild Charter section but I'll give you a brief run over of them. You must be at least level 20. We are a good/neutral guild so if you are of an evil class or race you must meet certain criteria which is basically having good faction in 3 good cities. You must earn 5 votes from our members and attend 2 of our events. <br>
<br>
We are currently recruiting all classes and races so if you are interested in joining a family fun environment I encourage you to take a look at the website and the message boards. Anyone wishing to be placed in the Quest of the Hopeful either contact myself or any of the other High Council or Officers (list can be found in Guild members section at the link above) in game and we will post you in the quest. <br>
<br>
I wish all future hopefuls good luck and I look forward to meeting and talking to you in-game.  <p><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=491453">Laennie Trueheart</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
